<plot>The United States and Britain are preparing to wage war on Iraq, for its undisclosed weapons of mass destruction, but Israel's nuclear, biological and chemical capabilities have yet remained un-inspected. Meanwhile Mordechai Vanunu has been imprisoned for 16 years for exposing Israel's secret nuclear bomb factory to the world back in the 1980's and is seen as a traitor in his own country. This film is the story of the nuclear-bomb, Vanunu and Israel's wall of silence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?269535</url></doc>
